---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | RealtyC — Real Estate AI Copilot" description="Privacy policy for realtycopilot.app — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>RealtyC ("we", "our") operates realtycopilot.app — AI-powered calculators and tools for real estate professionals. Contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@realtycopilot.app">privacy@realtycopilot.app</a></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Calculator inputs:</strong> Values you enter into our calculators (mortgage amounts, purchase prices, rental income) are processed in your browser and are not stored on our servers.</p>
    <p><strong>Analytics data:</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymized usage data including pages visited, session duration, and general geographic location (country/region). This data does not identify you personally.</p>
    <p><strong>Cookies:</strong> Google Analytics sets cookies to distinguish users and sessions. You can opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To understand how visitors use our tools and improve them</li>
      <li>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <p>If you are in the EU, UK, or California, you have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold. Email <a href="mailto:privacy@realtycopilot.app">privacy@realtycopilot.app</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Analytics data is retained for 14 months. No calculation inputs are stored after your browser session ends.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>Material changes will be noted with an updated date above.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
